[[!meta title="The Messenger"]]
[[!tag books books/espionage]]

Yet another of Silva's books on Allon.  This is the first one in which
Allon is active in the Office from the beginning, and one of the most
complex plot lines for Silva. Allons relationships advance as well.  A
very enjoyable caper. 
